title: Romeo & Juliet - Shakespeare (BBC - Branagh, Gielgud, Jacobi)
description:
Audio Books : General : MP3/Variable : English


Shakespeare's tragic story of a forbidden love.


Here's the last of the three out of print, Renaissance Theatre performances from the BBC.

Romeo And Juliet stars Kenneth Branagh, Samantha Bond (Miss Money Penny from the newer James Bond films), Ian Holm, Derek Jacobi, Dame Judi Dench (also in the newer James Bond films!) and Sir John Gielgud.

Once again, music by Patrick Doyle (Henry V, Needful things, Dead Again, and others).


Enjoy and Seed!!
